heelset & Tires\r\no Cervélo Reserve with 32mm Carbon rims (IRW 24mm), TLR, DT350 HG11, CL disc\r\no Panaracer Gravel King SK TLR 700x38\r\n• Cockpit & Accessories\r\no Handlebar: Carbon AB09 16° Flared Carbon, 31.8mm, integrated routing; Cervélo bar tape\r\no Stem: Cervélo ST32 Alloy, 31.8, (for Cervélo D-shaped fork steerer tube, integrated routing)\r\no Seatpost: Cervélo SP19 Carbon 27.2mm round (48-54cm Zero offset, 56-61cm, 25mm setback)\r\no Saddle: Prologo Dimension Nack\r\no Cervélo accessories: Stem Faceplate Computer/Acc mount, Rear Accessory Mount, and Smartpak 400A Top Tube Storage Bag, Downtube Protector\r\n• Component specifics by frame size:\r\no 48cm Bar width: 38c-c, Stem length: 70mm, Crank length: 165mm\r\n• Colors: Five Black\r\n• Sizes: 48 cm\r\n• Weight: 18.69 lbs (56cm)\r\n\r\nGeometry\r\nSize\t48\r\nWheel Size\t700\r\nStack\t505mm\r\nReach\t370mm\r\nHead Angle\t71°\r\nSeat Angle\t74.5°\r\nTop Tube Length\t512mm\r\nHead Tube Length\t83mm\r\nStandover\t690mm\r\nFork Trail\t58.6mm\r\nFork Offset\t52mm\r\nBottom Bracket Drop\t78.5mm\r\nFront Center\t583mm\r\nWheelbase\t990mm\r\nChainstay Length\t420mm\r\n",
